2014-07-07  Cyril Lavier  <bainisteoir(at)davromaniak(dot)eu>
 * Release V0.2 :
   + Corrected the filename when doing a united backup.
   + Fixed the crash when backing up mailboxes with special characters in their names using the --locale argument.
   + Added backup of mail filters in sieve format.
   + Added retention time in days.
   + Added the possibility to choose a custom destination folder.

